name: A simple blessing
description: All pieces are direct from the artist to you. Hand made and original. Steel cut picture hanger mounted on back for easy hanging. Celtic knot cross with gothic font. Cut from 16 gauge cold rolled steel. Painted black & green. Applied to a beautiful slab of western red cedar & finished with a gloss lacquer. aprox. 14" wide X 24" tall. Made to order. Please allow one week for fabrication. Red cedar & spalted big leaf maple available at this price. Be sure to contact us with your custom needs.(each piece sold is original in respect to the slab.)
